dc_description_s: This data layer represents public land survey system (PLSS) corners for Taylor County, Wisconsin in 2020. [Coordinates of PLSS corners supplied by the Taylor County Surveyor. Data collected by direct observation using survey grade GPS. Coordinates entered manually by GIS Specialist to create GIS point file. PLSS section created and subdivided by GIS Specialist.]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison.
